KANO: The crisis in the ruling All Peoples Congress (APC) took a new turn on Thursday (today) as the Federal High Court, Kano set aside a ruling of the FCT, Abuja High Court suspending Comrade Adams Oshiomhole, national chairman of the party. Justice Lewis Allagoa on Thursday ordered the police and Department of State Service (DSS) to provide security for Oshiomhole to resume in his office. Details laterâ€¦